Pytest
-------
Directory ---- Package---- Libarary

1.Create the test files and test function
2.Create the test packages
3.Create the test suites
4.test case, test file run
5.test file and test case skip
6. test file and test case xfail
7. Perticular test case and test file run.
8.Multiple test case run at a single time.
9.Plugin use
10. Parallel Test file run
11. Report generate


