Features

1.Innovacation

    command line Interface(CLI)
    Test Discovery
    JUnit Style , XML type report generating(Jenkins)
    Pytest support all kind of python codes
    Skipping tests

2.Asserations

    >assert :- comparison :- excepted result and outcome result comparison
    >Python support some Basic assert statement
    >Custom assertion comparision

3.Parameterized Tests --- DDT(Data Driven Test)

4.Fixture (Setup and teardown) :- built,custom and classic

5.Mocking :- enviroment

6.Pluglings(Parallel test) and Hooks :- pytest-xdist


#Import marker :-
markers are used to add metadata to your test functions.
They provide a way to categorize and selectively run tests based on
their assigned markers. Pytest allows you to define

type of marker
skip,skipif,xfail,customer marker, parametize


pytest
pytest -v -s (all data)

pytest -k test_file_name (perticular test file)
pytest -k test_math_operation

-m :- custome marker run
pytest -k test_math_operation -m smoke -v -s













